            "text": "Olive & June manicure kit"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". I've been a life-long nail biter, but I stop whenever my nails are painted. Going to get my nails done regularly is not in our budget, so I decided to purchase this manicure kit to try to do my nails regularly at home. Usually my nails are a mess when I try to paint my own, but the tools in this kit along with their tips have really helped me to do a much better at-home manicure."
