              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) My boys got big boy haircuts this month! Carson's hair is wavy, so I've always left it long because I liked that look at him. Caden's hair is stick straight, but because I was used to Carson's being long, I just kept Caden's long out of habit. But I realized both their hair was always in their face, so I decided to let the hair stylist use the trimmers. Caden's haircut was much shorter than Carson's, and it suddenly transformed him from a baby to a big toddler. I definitely shed tears, but I do think he looks super cute. :)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) My mom and dad took the boys for a weekend, and they took another fun trip to Sea World!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) A daddy and his youngest... :)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/SFTM_August-2021_EverydayAccountsBlog.com_3.png",
              "alt": "SFTM_August 2021_EverydayAccountsBlog.com",
              "title": null
