            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SFTM_August-2021_EverydayAccountsBlog.com_3.png",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (1) My other grandmother is very sick, so we made the journey to East Texas to visit with her and my grandfather. It's Christmas year-round at their house, so Carson and Caden both got to play with the Christmas train!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) They also enjoyed playing basketball with their great-grandpa in the driveway and exploring their old sewing shop."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) My mother- and father-in-law came for a visit one weekend, and we really enjoyed the family time."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) While they were here, Daniel and Carson snuck away for a very full day at the Kalahari Resort waterpark! We had gone here previously for Carson's birthday this past April, and he couldn't stop talking about it all summer. So, Daniel surprised him with a day in his favorite place!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
