                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(1) We got a couple date nights out this month and had fun exploring some new places in Austin!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(2) Caden wants to be "
