              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/2015/07/lazy-days-with-banana-08/",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Banana's"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " best friend so badly, but we are working on learning how to be gentle and that it's not a friendly thing to pull his tail, ha!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(3) Carson has put his face to the ground to watch wheels on toy vehicles since before he was one. I love that he still does this as a 3.5 year old."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "(4) On our trip back home from East Texas, we stopped at Baylor's campus to walk around. Here are the boys checking out the spot where Daniel proposed to me 11 years ago!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Have a fabulous September. I decided that autumn starts on September 1st here, so it's officially the start of my favorite months of the year!"
